name: Saja
description: Saja embodies the perfect fusion of K-pop idol charisma and supernatural warrior strength. His character represents the innovative concept of "K-pop Demon Hunters" where entertainment and demon hunting coexist. With his magnetic personality and powerful abilities, Saja stands out as a compelling character who navigates both the glamorous world of K-pop and the dangerous realm of supernatural threats.
